data.title: Wales Music: Katherine Jenkins releasing new album
data.meta_description: Welsh mezzo-soprano Katherine Jenkins has recorded her eighth album in Los Angeles and London with the help of Take That producer John Shanks. Katherine Jenkins Daydream is scheduled for release...
